comments: Brown (BOS) momentarily places his hand on Grimes' (NYK) side as the pick is set and marginal contact occurs as Grimes is rolling toward the rim.
Horford (BOS) slightly extends his arm into Barrett (NYK) as the pick is being set, and marginal contact occurs as Horford rolls toward the rim.
Horford (BOS) and Randle (NYK) come together and incidental contact occurs as both players go to pursue the loose ball.
Horford (BOS) reaches in and initiates contact with Brunson's (NYK) wrist, which causes him to lose control of the ball during his shooting motion.
Randle (NYK) moves alongside Tatum's (BOS) path and maintains a legal guarding position while contesting Tatum's drive toward the rim.
The ball is loose when the shot clock expires and a 24 second violation is correctly called.
Horford (BOS) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Grimes (NYK) moves alongside Tatum's (BOS) path and maintains a legal guarding position while contesting the shot attempt.
Sims (NYK) makes contact with the ball when he contests Williams III's (BOS) shot attempt, and the follow-through contact with Williams III's hand/wrist is incidental.
Sims (NYK) and Williams III (BOS) mutually engage and disengage as both players position themselves for the rebound.
Randle (NYK) moves into Brogdon (BOS) and affects his SQBR as he attempts to control the loose ball.
Horford (BOS) does not allow Grimes (NYK) time and distance to avoid the pick.
Brown (BOS) steps forward while defending Brunson's (NYK) drive toward the rim and the contact is marginal.
Sims (NYK) gathers the ball and takes three steps before starting his dribble.
Williams III (BOS) moves alongside Randle's (NYK) path and maintains a legal guarding position while contesting the driving shot attempt.
Randle (NYK) and Tatum (BOS) engage in marginal contact as both players position themselves for the rebound.
Tatum (BOS) reaches in and initiates contact with Randle's (NYK) arm as he attempts to gain possession of the loose ball.
Tatum's (BOS) hand slides off of Sims' (NYK) side and marginal contact occurs as he is moving underneath the pick.
Barrett (NYK) makes incidental contact with Horford's (BOS) hand as both players pursue the loose ball.
Randle (NYK) moves alongside Tatum's (BOS) path and maintains a legal guarding position while contesting the driving shot attempt.
Barrett (NYK) moves alongside Brown's (BOS) path and maintains a legal guarding position while contesting the driving shot attempt.
Williams III (BOS) initiates contact with Randle (NYK) at the end of his drive affecting his SQBR as he attempts to pass the ball.
Williams III (BOS) firms up in Grimes' (NYK) path as the pick is being set.
Brunson (NYK) moves into Brown (BOS) and initiates contact that affects his jump shot attempt.
Horford (BOS) commits a take foul on Barrett (NYK).
Horford (BOS) firms up in Barrett's (NYK) path as the screen is being set.
Brunson (NYK) cleanly blocks Brogdon's (BOS) shot attempt.
